sql: CREATE TABLE Users (UserID DOUBLE NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY, FullName VARCHAR(35) NOT NULL, EmailAddress VARCHAR(35) NOT NULL, Password VARCHAR(70) NOT NULL);

CREATE TABLE Contacts (ContactID DOUBLE NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY, EmailAddress VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL, FirstName VARCHAR(50), LastName VARCHAR(50), DNDEmailBounce BOOLEAN, Comments VARCHAR(250));
